Deny Amnesty Credits Act of 2015 

This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to deny the earned income tax credit and the child tax credit to any illegal alien&#160;who has received employment authorization under a program for deferred action on removal that has not been not specifically authorized by law.</summary>
